reviews.review_text:
sometimes the light's all shinin' on me-e-e hey now, at last we got a sbd from this show... I was looking for(ward)... okay, there ARE better sounding ones, but compared to the inferior earlier versions this one is...FAIR! So be grateful that you're NOT dead...haha...
it's not so bad not to exactly hear the voices, because of the MUSIC. Long for the play, not for the sound, and the sun is comin'up,innit?

Put'ErThere!!! notesto self:

pretty poor quality audio overall....but no worse than those cassettes you listened to when you was trippin around the country ... you monkey-head!!!  Those tapes saved me

o.k.   add this to your dark star collection . ..
the boyz are chasing down a porkipine with both eyes covered

as usual... can't give anything in the archive anything but 5-star ... if it is by the Dead then it gets hoisted
warning cassette hiss I didn't find it listenable.
- Wish we still had the soundboards.
